A game-clinching block. A game-clinching dunk. 34.3 pts, 10.3 reb, and 3.3 blk in his last three full games.

@antdavis23 had himself quite a week.

node.text: On this day in 18 years ago, Chick made his way into the history books.
Somebody say #NBAHandlesWeek?
